{"tid":1152362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會內受襲重創 范國威今報警","createTime":"2019-05-13T02:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T03:22:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4772df29031691ee9204a5781c2254fa5119f24d","tid":1152362,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:07:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190513/20677171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F20677171&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=8205c8ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F20677171&h=bb4430c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190513/20677171</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年05月13日 <br />\n<br />\n立會內受襲重創 范國威今報警<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190513/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190513%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=3d1da93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n范國威昨在fb上載照片透露已出院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在前日立法會送中惡法會議衝突受到重創的議員范國威，昨在facebook貼文透露情況無大礙並已出院，今日會與新民主同盟成員報警，跟進今次在立法會內受到暴力對待的事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陳太：港英從未擬商中港引渡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n檢查後無發現腦震盪<br />\n<br />\n范國威昨午在fb發文指已出院，前日他在立法會和建制派拉扯後從高處墮下失去知覺，被送到瑪麗醫院急症室，經腦掃描及照頸椎X光後，沒有發現頭骨受損及腦震盪，但因為持續頭暈及頭痛，被轉送到神經外科病房留院觀察，經休息後他前晚已清醒，頭暈及頭痛症狀已消失。他昨天中午在醫生了解過身體狀況後安排出院，今日會聯同新同盟成員到警署就受襲事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n漁農界立法會議員、民建聯何俊賢在facebook發文，指《蘋果日報》昨日一篇題為〈被何俊賢推倒 范國威需照腦〉報道中，說他「雙手推開范令他倒地」、「當范被何俊賢推開時一失平衡」失實及誤導，但何在聲明中只說報道「漠視當時由反對派議員刻意造成的混亂局面，以及范國威多次衝擊石禮謙議員的情況」，但未有否認報道指，范被他推倒而墮地受傷。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫劍弦  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n李柱銘：美加極擔憂送中 商界傳媒恐得罪北京「就作條罪告你」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n黃宏發：涂開會合憲 建制會議違規<br />\n<br />\n陳太：港英從未擬商中港引渡<br />\n李柱銘：美加極擔憂送中商界傳媒恐得罪北京「就作條罪告你」<br />\n黃宏發：涂開會合憲 建制會議違規<br />\n律政司前高官反駁鄭若驊：港人港審無違人權法"},{"pid":"fc554924aa4c5b3627a02403558f499f388d7b38","tid":1152362,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2125d1a19a02a8c49c6dbce1c202d99713fbe507","tid":1152362,"uid":228963,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf77a8375c2ac87f413c3c7bfbe1841feb98e2c0","tid":1152362,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":44,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"佢自己飛身上人堆，咎由自取？"},{"pid":"044396fb5c6c0dcfe37195ed8e5056b0ec2d00c8","tid":1152362,"uid":64009,"like":3,"dislike":35,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"做下show又階段性勝利<br />\n比d掌聲自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428371fa5cefd10228d978bd0379909ec57e2f26","tid":1152362,"uid":42188,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛黑色警告信號現正生效</span></span>"},{"pid":"0a5f30a9a15900b3ad468724ed61ddbbbf9901b2","tid":1152362,"uid":77180,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"044396fb5c6c0dcfe37195ed8e5056b0ec2d00c8","tid":1152362,"uid":64009,"like":3,"dislike":35,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"做下show又階段性勝利<br />\n比d掌聲自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:25:43.000Z","msg":"對面做唔通自己唔做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c22ebd5a422f05cb41777053df17e4d73180444","tid":1152362,"uid":34410,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"2125d1a19a02a8c49c6dbce1c202d99713fbe507","tid":1152362,"uid":228963,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02: